snippet.title: Hidden Cats in Spooky Town
snippet.description: It's Halloween time! Do you choose Trick or Cat? Find all the Hidden Cats one by one in the Spooky Town to reveal the final colored art. Play through different modes, find special cats, and unlock bonus levels! More than 970 hidden objects to find! Now with the extra bonus level, AFTER PARTY!
